videos.headline: Staiti leads Georgia to second round of NCAA Tournament
videos.description: Jenna Staiti scores 19 points with nine rebounds to lead the 6-seeded Bulldogs over 11-seed Dayton for a 70-54 win to advance in the NCAA Tournament.
